</p>
<p>
<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
    &lt;link href="/js/mapnager/mapnager.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"&gt;
    &lt;script src='/js/mapnager/mapnager.js' type='text/javascript'&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
